bilingual.source: We need a sheet for the new bed.
bilingual.target: 我们需要一张新的床单。

bilingual.source: There is a small bloodstain on the sheet.
bilingual.target: 这张床单上有一个小血迹。
我想要我的床上有床单。

bilingual.source: This sheet has a tear in it.
She stretched the sheet out to dry.

bilingual.target: 老师：那床单上面是啥子？

bilingual.source: He left a dollar under my sheet.
bilingual.target: 他在我的床单下放了一块钱。

list.abstract: sheet是显示在workbook窗口中的表格。一个sheet可以由1048576行和2464列构成。行的编号从1到65536，列的编号依次用字母A、B ……IV表示。 行号显示在工作簿窗口的左边，列号显示在工作簿窗口的上边。Excel默认一个工作簿有三个sheet，用户可以根据需要添加sheet，但每一个工作簿最多可以包括255个sheet。 每个sheet有一个名字，sheet名显示在工作表标签上。工作表标签显示了系统默认的前三个sheet名：Sheet1、Sheet2、Sheet3。 sheet是Excel存储和处理数据的最重要的部分，其中包含排列成行和列的单元格。它是工作簿的一部分，也称电子表格。使用sheet可以对数据进行组织和分析。可以同时在多张sheet上输入并编辑数据，并且可以对来自不同工作表的数据进行汇总计算。在创建图表之后，既可以将其置于源数据所在的工作表上，也可以放置在单独的图表工作表上。

yingyinNormal.en: Penny's brain teaser this morning. She and Koothrappali emerge from your bedroom. She is disheveled, and Raj is dressed only in a sheet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩妮今早留下的头脑风暴悬念，她跟库萨帕里从你的卧室走出，她衣衫不整，拉杰只裹了个床单。

yingyinNormal.en: The melting ice in question is the Antarctic ice sheet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里讨论的融冰是南极的冰盖。

yingyinNormal.en: The tunnel is the last thing on the activity sheet. Hooray!
yingyinNormal.zh: 通道是清单上面最后一项了。噢耶！

yingyinNormal.en: Can't do what? She says take our names off the sign-in sheet and leave.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不能做什么？她叫我们把名字擦掉直接走人。

yingyinNormal.en: But even doing all this after two months, I still didn't have time to work my way up a sheet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尽管如此2个月后，我连一张名单都没打完。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, make a contact sheet of these frames as soon as you can. And don't say anything to anyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，用最快方式把这些都洗出来，别跟任何人说。

yingyinNormal.en: Honey, it's Christmas Eve. Who even knows you're in there? No, our names are on the sign-in sheet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的，今天是圣诞节前夜，谁会知道你们在那里，我们在签到表上签名。

yingyinNormal.en: The tunnel is the last thing on the activity sheet. Hooray! Last stop. All change, everybody off now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 隧道是最后一个需要找的东西。太棒了！终点站到了。全部下车了，现在大家都下车吧。

yingyinNormal.en: The children have to spot everything that is on the activity sheet. A boat. A signal box. And a tunnel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 孩子们要找出活动表格中所有的东西。一条船。一个信号盒。还有一条通道。

yingyinNormal.en: Ice loss to the West Antarctic Ice Sheet has increased by a factor of three on a yearly basis since 2009.
yingyinNormal.zh: 西南极冰盖自2009年起，基于三个因素，每年融冰都增加。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. How about this? We open on a blank sheet of paper. Under a Mozart fugue, we suddenly see a drop of blood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧。那这样呢？我们打开一张白纸，在莫扎特的背景乐里，我们突然看到一滴血。

yingyinNormal.en: It wasn't even an official sign-up sheet. He printed it himself, and he put his name down on every slot for the next six months.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那甚至都不是正式的登记表格，他自己打印出来在每一个机位都写上自己的名字，使用六个月。

yingyinNormal.en: Here are your activity sheets. The children have to spot everything that is on the activity sheet. A boat. A signal box. And a tunnel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些是你们的活动表格。孩子们必须找到这个活动表格上的所有的东西。一艘船。一个信号灯。一条隧道。

yingyinNormal.en: There are charities that I support who wouldn't exist without me. If life is a balance sheet, and I think it is, why, I believe I'm in credit!
yingyinNormal.zh: 很多慈善机构如果不是因为我根本不会存在于世。如果人生是负债表，我认为确实是，那么，我还有盈余。

yingyinNormal.en: If you have any questions, here's the FAQ sheet, or if you prefer the human touch, I do a live web chat called Apartment Talk on Tuesday nights.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如有任何问题，这里列出了常见问题的答案，若你更喜欢人性化解答，每周四晚我提供公寓问题的在线聊天服务。

yingyinNormal.en: Here's the problem. I was clearly signed up to use the mainframe in Buckman 204, and Dr. Winkle just wantonly ripped the sign-up sheet off the wall.
yingyinNormal.zh: 问题是这样，我很明确地做了登记来使用博克曼实验室204室的主机，而温克尔博士却粗暴地把它们都撕了下来。

yingyinNormal.en: The same thing I've been doing for three days. Trying to figure out why electrons behave as if they have no mass when traveling through a graphene sheet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 做我这三天一直在做的工作，想要弄明白为什么电子在穿过石墨烯时会表现得像是没有质量一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Scientists looking at the ice sheet often divide it into catchment basins to better understand how the ice in each basin changes and discharges into the ocean, and it turns out to be quite a bit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 观察冰原的科学家常把冰原分成许多集水区，以便了解各集水区的变化和观察流到海里的过程，结果非常惊人。

examination_example.sentence: The only components required, though, are a 5'×5' <highlight>sheet</highlight> of clear or slightly milky plastic, six feet of plastic tube, and a container.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 不过，唯一需要的组件是一块5英尺×5英尺的的透明或微乳白色塑料板、六英尺长的塑料管和一个容器。

examination_example.sentence: Ground water evaporates (蒸发) and collects on the <highlight>sheet</highlight> until small drops of water form, run down the material.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 地面水蒸发，聚集在板材上，直到形成小水滴，顺着材料流下来。

examination_example.sentence: Next, cover the hole with the plastic <highlight>sheet</highlight>, securing the edges of the plastic with dirt.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 接下来，用塑料布盖住洞，用泥土固定塑料布的边缘。

examination_example.sentence: On the same <highlight>sheet</highlight> of paper, write or type your name, address, telephone number, and birth date.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在同一张纸上写下或键入你的姓名、地址、电话号码和出生日期。

examination_example.sentence: Write by hand or type on a single <highlight>sheet</highlight> of paper.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一张纸上手写或打字。
